        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/l/4491bb/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2025-12-03T11:48:09.733Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Agreed, and also wondering if this is still relevant:</p>\n<aside class=\"quote quote-modified\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"48759\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/b3f665/48.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <div class=\"quote-title__text-content\">\n      <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/make-release-notes-chat-visible-even-if-you-dont-have-6-chats/48759\">Make release notes chat visible even if you don't have 6 chats</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/android-feature-requests/18\"><span data-category-id=\"18\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #2D8B39; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF; --parent-category-badge-color: #83B72A;\" data-parent-category-id=\"17\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category --style-square --has-parent\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Android Feature Requests</span></span></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    Hallo.  I want to suggest that “Relase Notes” feature should be active 24/7 and every Signal user should get this feature. \nIf users those have six chats or more than six chats are receiving this feature which is not good.  Every Signal user should get this feature.  Most of us are not receiving this feature because either we don’t have any chat (don’t have contacts on Signal/very few contacts are on Signal) or less than six chats on Signal. \nWhatsApp is going to relase this feature too for ever…\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n\n<p>Originally I thought that not receiving the official Signal updates chat on iOS was a bug, and then I thought it was the issue above issue after moving from Android to iOS. However, I’ve had more than 6 chats for a while now so that I should have gotten at least the recent announcement about polls.</p>\n<p>Is there an official announcement chat in iOS but it just isn’t updated when relevant new releases ship? Or doesn’t it exist in the first place?</p>",
        "post_number": 2,
        "post_type": 1,
